description: Refrigerator Flipper Assembly ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 13 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11708993 Manufacturer Part Number AGU74110902 The main top guide pin guides the main top onto the body of the range and helps hold the top in position.

installationInstructions.author: Michael from EASTLAKE, OH
installationInstructions.title: Spring broke on flapper door
installationInstructions.content: Took 2 screws out , pushed flapper up, unhooked wire connector, reversed to install new door. Less than 5 minutes. So easy , a caveman could do it.
